| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-5102 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ab3f0cad-5c34-5f12-858d-c34b17b512a1"
